{
  "texts": [
    "A comprehensive list of the feature vectors can be found in the literature: 20.",
    "Excess feature vectors in the test set were excluded to maintain consistency, aligning it with the training dataset.",
    "Consequently, neither the training nor the test datasets contained missing values.",
    "Categorical data were mapped to numerical integer values.",
    "Imbalanced dataset distributions were addressed by conferring inverse frequency weights upon the data."
  ]
}